  "statement": "Brain view lists a change's entities and workflows, grouped by kind. Within a change's thread, the app SHALL list the entities and workflows the agent has created for that change, **grouped by kind**, read-only. - *Acceptance:* For a change with two requirements and one workflow, the brain view shows a requirements group with two items and a workflows group with one item. - *Design-stage follow-up:* grouping-by-kind is the confirmed default for now; the grouping/sorting is to be refined in the design-stage whole-surface visual UX pass (recorded under Design-stage constraints)",
